      section#about
        h2 OSID Hack-a-thon
        #aboutHackathon(style='height:200px;font-size:16px;')
          p OSID Club at DA-IICT, Gandhinagar announces it's first annual hackathon event. We are gathering the best hackers in the West India region for 24 hours to socialize with fellow hackers and build awesome stuff. You make teams up and compete with other teams for astounding prizes. 
          p <i>Show us your hacking chops while we pamper you with great food and drinks.</i> We will be catering to all your needs from food to internet connectivity.
          p Hackathon is a very demanding environment where one collaborates and competes simultaneously. Ideas germinated during the hackathon may become tomorrow's great tools and technologies, and we want to facilitate this process. Expect to meet hackers who share your interests, and potential job opportunities from our sponsors.
      //section#announcements
